      • acronym

        public String acronym(String camelCased)
        Returns an acronym string for a camel-cased string. The acronym is a string of all upper-case and digit characters in the original string. It will not begin itself with a digit.
        Parameters:
        camelCased - The argument string -- should be in camel case (via a call to unmangle) but not required.
        Returns:
        acronym
